commit.message:
varray.h (VARRAY_PUSH_GENERIC_PTR, [...]): Fix macro argument typo.

2000-06-01  Stan Cox  <scox@cygnus.com>
	* varray.h (VARRAY_PUSH_GENERIC_PTR, VARRAY_PUSH_CHAR_PTR): Fix
	macro argument typo.

From-SVN: r34346

files.patch:
@@ -1,3 +1,8 @@
+2000-06-01  Stan Cox  <scox@cygnus.com>
+
+	* varray.h (VARRAY_PUSH_GENERIC_PTR, VARRAY_PUSH_CHAR_PTR): Fix
+	macro argument typo.
+
 2000-06-01  Zack Weinberg  <zack@wolery.cumb.org>
 
 	* cpplex.c (maybe_macroexpand): Use CPP_WTRADITIONAL.  Improve

@@ -239,8 +239,8 @@ extern void varray_check_failed PARAMS ((varray_type, size_t,
 #define VARRAY_PUSH_ULONG(VA, X)	VARRAY_PUSH (VA, ul, X)
 #define VARRAY_PUSH_WIDE_INT(VA, X)	VARRAY_PUSH (VA, hint, X)
 #define VARRAY_PUSH_UWIDE_INT(VA, X)	VARRAY_PUSH (VA, uhint, X)
-#define VARRAY_PUSH_GENERIC_PTR(VA,N)	VARRAY_PUSH (VA, generic, X)
-#define VARRAY_PUSH_CHAR_PTR(VA,N)	VARRAY_PUSH (VA, cptr, X)
+#define VARRAY_PUSH_GENERIC_PTR(VA, X)	VARRAY_PUSH (VA, generic, X)
+#define VARRAY_PUSH_CHAR_PTR(VA, X)	VARRAY_PUSH (VA, cptr, X)
 #define VARRAY_PUSH_RTX(VA, X)		VARRAY_PUSH (VA, rtx, X)
 #define VARRAY_PUSH_RTVEC(VA, X)	VARRAY_PUSH (VA, rtvec, X)
 #define VARRAY_PUSH_TREE(VA, X)		VARRAY_PUSH (VA, tree, X)
